NBA, Players Union Complete Draft of Labor Agreement; Vote Ends Tomorrow

-- B y   M a s o n   L e v i n s o n
-- 
2011-12-07T21:29:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-07/nba-players-union-complete-draft-of-labor-agreement-vote-ends-tomorrow.html
The  National Basketball Association 
and its players completed the details for a new labor agreement
that calls for the season to start Dec. 25.  Players will vote on the deal until 4 p.m. tomorrow. Owners
will vote at a meeting in  New York  tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mason Levinson in New York at 
 mlevinson@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
